  "headline": "Personal Finance",
  "description": "Personal finance fundamentals: spend less than you earn, invest the difference, avoid debt, build emergency fund (3-6 months expenses), diversify investments. Index fund investing (Bogle, Vanguard): low-cost, broad market exposure beats stock picking long-term. Compound interest is the most powerful force in personal finance. Start early.",
